<p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">2024年3月5日下午，经济管理学院积极响应“最干净校园”行动，学院组织了教室卫生大扫除活动。志愿者按照要求对教室卫生进行重点清扫，以实际行动为创建“最干净校园”助力。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713363889044052504.png" title="1713363889044052504.png" alt="image.png" width="369" height="330" style="width: 369px; height: 330px;"/></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在学院的组织下，学生党员、入党积极分子、学生会以及学生代表参加了本次活动。本次活动打扫的区域包括教室、学院大厅、学院各层走廊、楼梯、办公室、公共教室、党员活动室等地方。同学们全力以赴，通过共同努力，使得每个区域都焕然一新。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500868418057490.png" title="1717500868418057490.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500877347058498.png" title="1717500877347058498.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500892223084256.png" title="1717500892223084256.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500901923093283.png" title="1717500901923093283.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500917886000902.png" title="1717500917886000902.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500928442030133.png" title="1717500928442030133.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500938342035858.png" title="1717500938342035858.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500951447086071.png" title="1717500951447086071.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500963997001263.png" title="1717500963997001263.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500974922074351.png" title="1717500974922074351.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">同学们对教室的风扇、门窗、地面卫生以及桌椅、物品摆放情况进行了细致的清理，劳动认真而专注，虽然挂着汗水，脸上却都流露出快乐的笑容。经过同学们的细致打扫下，窗台的边角、讲台的缝隙。每个角落都变得干干净。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717500997590071507.png" title="1717500997590071507.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240604/1717501012129015333.png" title="1717501012129015333.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在学院的组织下，学生党员、入党积极分子、学生会以及学生代表参加了本次活动。本次活动打扫的区域包括教室、学院大厅、学院各层走廊、楼梯、办公室、</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 2em;">公共教室、党员活动室等地方。同学们全力以赴，通过共同努力，使得每个区域都焕然一新。</span></p>